---
title: One-Pot Tortellini Wonder with Kale and Parmesan Breadcrumbs
description: In this recipe, our chefs managed to strike a balance between comfort and nutrition by combining creamy cheese tortellini with kale, and finishing it off with a crispy panko Parmesan topping. But perhaps the best part about it all is that this dinner requires minimal pots and pans. One, to be exact.
